(lively orchestral music)
(traffic rumbling)

2
00:00:09,474 --> 00:00:12,265
(lively orchestral music fades)

3
00:00:12,265 --> 00:00:15,265
(upbeat jazz music)

4
00:00:16,148 --> 00:00:19,034
(David laughing)

5
00:00:19,034 --> 00:00:19,884
- (laughing) Ooh!

6
00:00:21,515 --> 00:00:23,148
Ooh! (laughs)

7
00:00:23,148 --> 00:00:27,396
(upbeat jazz music continues)

8
00:00:27,396 --> 00:00:32,396
(vehicle pedals squeaking)
